      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ESTRADA (2) is better than last start when sixth (19.74) in a Mix 6/7 H at Healesville over 350m. Tough to beat if on-song. CHEER DOWN (5) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (29.22) in a Bottom Up - Grade 6 at Bendigo. Form here at the trip excellent including two wins. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Can do much better this time. NITRO MOSES (1) turned in a moderate run last time when eighth at Healesville over 300m behind Proud Mary (17.49) in a Bottom Up - Grade 7. Form from his last run is proving strong. Key player if finds best. GRANTVILLE FLYER (7) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
